        <profileDesc>
            <creation> Not before <date>1563</date>, not after <date>1597</date>.
            </creation>
            <abstract>
                <p>A collection of chants close to the Dǝggwā but not identical with it. The colophon tells that the
                work was compiled by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12652Gera">ʾabbā  Gera</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12654HablaSellase">ʾabbā
                Habla Śǝllāse</persName> from a number of Dǝggʷā witnesses,
              following the order of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe">King Śarḍa Dǝngǝl</persName>.</p>
            </abstract>
